 him and the main tank or any other actual PC.<br>
<br>
As far as mages in groups, I love them!  Situational burst DPS is very nice, and the pet is good sustained DPS.  In particular, I prefer mages in my groups to use air pets in groups, because the stuns can really slow down mob DPS which makes my job a lot easier, and I cannot recall a time when a pet has taken aggro from the MT. <p>Zarros Livinglight<br>
